prod1 = Product('msft', 'mICRoSOFT')
prod2 = Product('MSFT', 'Microsoft')
assert prod1 == prod2
assert (prod1 != prod2) is False
prod1 = Product('AAPL', 'Apple')
prod2 = Product('MSFT', 'Microsoft')
assert (prod1 == prod2) is False
assert prod1 != prod2
prod1 = Product('msft', 'mICRoSOFT')
prod2 = Product('MSFT', 'Microsoft')
assert (prod1 == prod2) is True
assert prod1 == prod2
prod1 = Product('msft', 'mICRoSOFT')
prod2 = Product('MSFT', 'Microsoft')
prod2.set_identifier('CUSIP', '20200')
prod1.set_identifier('CUSIP', '23222')
assert (prod1 == prod2) is False
assert prod1 != prod2
